snippet.title: Graham Plowman - Composer
snippet.description:
Showcasing the work of H.P. Lovecraft and wider Cthulhu Mythos music composer, Graham Plowman.

Horror music, Cthulhu music, Lovecraftian music, scary and dark music...It's what I do. All released music is available on iTunes, Bandcamp, Spotify, Amazon, and many other platforms. I also compose for film, games and generally any other media.

Contact me through email (click the button below to see my email address).
